ComicInfo.Title: I Want My Mommaaaaa!!; Overture
ComicInfo.Summary:
I Want My Mommaaaaa!!: Caitlin finds a little girl lost at the fair and tries to reunite her with her mother before the tyke drives her crazy.
Overture: With Freefall and Rainmaker having run off to find Roxy's stepmother, Lynch sends Alex out to bring them in. Warblade and Grifter are visiting Isaiah when a huge monster breaks through the wall and captures their friend. Alex shows up at Ms. Spaulding's house to bring in the girls when, much to Roxy's surprise, her stepmother seems to know him. Their reunion is cut short, however, when they are attacked by Warhawks. Ivana shows up to take over I.O. operations.
